Class GVRStatsLine

  • java.lang.Object

        public void printLine(long periodMS)
        Log a line with a specified frequency. If the method is invoked before periodMS millisecond has passed since last printing, the new line is suppressed. The periodMS can be set to 0 to print every line.
        Parameters:
        periodMS - The log period in milliseconds.
